$ Registry: HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Power

The value *HibernateEnabled* determines if *hibernation* is enabled:
code {
reg query HKLM\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Power /v HibernateEnabled
code }

sa:

  The subkey → Windows/registry/tree/HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE/System/CurrentControlSet/Control/Power/PowerSettings[`PowerSettings`]

 `→ Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/powercfg_exe`
